2. make sure to npm install firebase: https://firebase.google.com/docs/web/setup
and give your email to Huang who is the owner of the firebase db.

3. when running the app, 'inspect' the code and set the ratio to phone size

4. for each page if you want to retrive the data from db, 
make user to use "useEffect" -- look at ProfileContainer.js for details.

5. search for "TODO" and see if there is anything thing needed to be implemented
notice this is not a comprehensive list of things, so there could be more to do.